Ak! I forgot about the post with Icedragon! Sorry.

* Iron Raptor suddenly looked towards Icedragon as he came up to her, her 
systems listening carfully once he mantioned the maximal matrix.
She looked down at the device and lifted a brow. This was given to the best 
Maximals?
< Fat chance for that.> she thought. There were better Maximals then her, 
she was positive. But for some dumb reason she had been chosen for 3rd in 
command then then was stuck with the role of comamnder.
She didn't mind it, it had all just been so sudden. She was still trying to 
get use to it.
But then she heard of Icedragon's phrase about having to put it into her 
spark, looking right at her chest right away.
She had no chambers or anything in her body that she could just open up and 
stick this in. It was all one solid piece now.
< Guess there's disadvantages to everything.> But she made it a note to do 
this later, even if it meant surgery.*
